I am most willing to instruct you in the correct methods of conducting this campaign.  Click the arrows at the top of this message to view additional instructions. If you feel capable of conducting this campaign on your own, close this message, right-click on my image in the Command Center and select `Agent Advice' from the pop-up menu. Should you later acknowledge a need for my assistance, follow the same procedure to reactivate `Agent Advice'.  You may access this message, as well as further instructions, by clicking on the Agent icon in the Message Alert bar located to the right of this message.